Program: The Forum
Title: The Benefits of Simplicity
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03k95ss
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 2 Mar 2016
The world might seem more complex by the day but there are practical steps which can make it less complicated again. Bridget Kendall talks to three people whose mission it is to make the world a simpler place through better design - designer Per Mollerup, software engineer Pieter Hintjens and art historian Timon Screech. (Photo: Red brush swirl on paper. Credit: Shan Pillay) Show less